# Demo / portfolio static-bundle workflow.
#   tmp/snapshot-raw  — UNSANITIZED captures of /api/* responses. Contains
#                       real names, real Slack IDs, real Jira keys, real
#                       Workday absence reasons. NEVER commit. Gitignoring
#                       defensively so a typo in a script can't leak.
#   dist/             — sanitized static bundle. Built by scripts/build-demo.mjs
#                       and pushed to the public `demo` branch via worktree.
#                       Living on `main` would just create churn diffs every
#                       time someone re-runs the build, so we keep it out
#                       of the main branch entirely.
tmp/
dist/
